{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_01","textHome":"我是百江渚的说！要自我介绍吗？@那么，就只要记住一件事就行了……@小渚最喜欢的食物就是奶酪！@是奶酪的说！不管是味道还是形状都最喜欢了！@有圆滚滚的，也有棱角分明的……@光是看着就兴致高涨的说！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.6,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_17","textHome":"虽然我在吹奏部选了小号，@但一开始我完全吹不出声音……@无论怎么吹都只有「嘶～」一个音……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":300}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_18","textHome":"有一天，我发现了！@用吃奶酪时的口型，小号就能吹出声音！@这是真的！@看！就是这种感觉的说！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":300}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_19","textHome":"嗯嗯……看来小渚的魔力又提高了的说！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":300}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_20","textHome":"好清爽的感觉……@还有我的肚子饿了的说！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":200}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_21","textHome":"我真正喜欢上奶酪，@是妈妈给我做奶酪蛋糕的时候。@那真是好美味的说……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200700,"motion":300}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_033.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_22","textHome":"妈妈只给我做过一次奶酪蛋糕。@之后就生病住院了，住院了也就做不了了，@而现在她已经不在人世了的说。@所以，那块奶酪蛋糕，@我再也没能吃上第二次的说……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":0}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_033.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_23","textHome":"爸爸在妈妈生病之后不久就失踪了的说。@不过……我记得在我吃妈妈做的奶酪蛋糕时，@爸爸妈妈都在我的眼前笑着的场景……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":300}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_ch